to%20shopping%2C%20timing%20is%20everything.%20Shopping%20too%20early%20or%20too%20late%20can%20make%20things%20difficult.%20If%20I've%20shopped%20too%20early%2C%20my%20kids%20want%20to%20wear%20their%20clothes%20before%20school%20starts.%20To%20avoid%20this%2C%20I%20have%20to%20set%20clear%20boundaries%20and%20expectations%20ahead%20of%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20kids%20may%20try%20on%20the%20back-to-school%20haul%20and%20show%20off%20to%20friends%20via%20Snapchat%20or%20TikTok%2C%20and%20then%20it%20is%20stocked%20away%20until%20school.%20The%20advantage%20of%20early%20shopping%20is%20the%20variety%20you%20will%20find.%20It%20also%20allows%20families%20to%20budget%20and%20take%20a%20specific%20amount%20out%20of%20paychecks%20throughout%20the%20summer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20few%20summers%20where%20I've%20waited%20until%20the%20last%20minute%20proved%20difficult.%20I%20tend%20to%20pay%20more%20because%20I%20feel%20pressured%2C%20the%20selection%20isn't%20as%20great%2C%20and%20I%20haven't%20been%20able%20to%20space%20money%20out%2C%20lessening%20the%20blow%20of%20one%20gigantic%20shopping%20spree.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20local%20salon%20has%20a%20back-to-school%20sale%20that%20kicks%20in%20the%20week%20before%20school%2C%20my%20kids%20have%20to%20wait%20for%20the%20haircut.%20I%20also%20plan%20on%20where%20to%20use%20my%20funds%20best%20and%20share%20that%20info%20with%20my%20kids.%20If%20they%20choose%20to%20spend%20more%20on%20school%20supplies%2C%20it%20will%20impact%20the%20amount%20they%20are%20allowed%20to%20spend%20on%20clothes.%20Normally%2C%20my%20kids%20prefer%20to%20spend%20on%20clothing%20and%20shoes%2C%20so%20picking%20up%20classroom%20supplies%20from%20the%20Dollar%20Store%20helps%20them%20and%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20mother%2C%20I'll%20take%20whatever%20tips%20I%20can%20to%20simplify%20our%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftips-back-to-school-shopping