%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Protests%20Over%20Sex%20Assault%20Of%204-Year-Olds%20In%20School%2C%20Stones%20Thrown%20At%20Cops%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETwo%20four-year-old%20girls%20were%20sexually%20assaulted%20at%20an%20English%20medium%20school%20by%20a%20cleaning%20staff%20in%20Maharashtra's%20Thane.%20The%20incident%20has%20triggered%20massive%20protests%2C%20with%20residents%20blocking%20the%20Mumbai%20rail%20route%20at%20Badalpur%20railway%20station%2C%20bringing%20train%20services%20to%20a%20standstill.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVisuals%20showed%20protesters%20pelting%20stones%20at%20cops%20as%20they%20fled%20across%20the%20railway%20tracks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20four-year-old%20girls%20were%20allegedly%20sexually%20assaulted%20by%20a%2023-year-old%20male%20cleaning%20staff%20member%20inside%20the%20girls'%20toilet%20at%20their%20school%20on%20August%2016.%20The%20accused%20has%20since%20been%20arrested%20after%20an%20FIR%20was%20filed%20against%20him.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20school's%20response%20to%20the%20incident%20has%20done%20little%20to%20quell%20the%20fury%20of%20the%20parents%20and%20local%20residents.%20Although%20the%20school%20administration%20has%20suspended%20the%20principal%20and%20dismissed%20the%20class%20teacher%20and%20nanny%20involved%2C%20parents%20remain%20dissatisfied.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20parents%20believe%20that%20the%20school%20has%20failed%20to%20take%20full%20responsibility%20for%20the%20safety%20of%20their%20children%2C%20and%20they%20are%20particularly%20incensed%20by%20the%20lack%20of%20an%20official%20apology%20or%20assurance%20from%20the%20school%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInvestigations%20by%20the%20police%20have%20uncovered%20significant%20lapses%20in%20the%20school's%20security%20measures.%20The%20probe%20has%20revealed%20that%20there%20were%20no%20female%20attendants%20present%20in%20the%20girls'%20toilets%2C%20a%20basic%20safety%20requirement%20in%20any%20educational%20setting.%20Addi