%3BSchool%26quot%3B%20Of%20Criminals%20In%20Madhya%20Pradesh%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThree%20remote%20villages%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20-%20Kadia%2C%20Gulkhedi%2C%20and%20Hulkhedi%20-%20have%20gained%20nationwide%20infamy%20as%20%26quot%3Bnurseries%26quot%3B%20of%20criminals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESituated%20about%20117%20kilometers%20from%20the%20state%20capital%2C%20Bhopal%2C%20these%20villages%20in%20the%20Rajgarh%20district%20are%20known%20for%20training%20children%20in%20the%20%26quot%3Barts%20of%20theft%2C%20robbery%2C%20and%20dacoity%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%2C%20even%20with%20their%20authority%2C%20are%20known%20to%20tread%20carefully%20in%20this%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Beginning%20Of%20Crime%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChildren%20as%20young%20as%2012%20or%2013%20are%20sent%20to%20these%20villages%20by%20their%20parents%20to%20be%20trained%20in%20criminal%20activities.%20The%20parents%2C%20after%20meeting%20with%20gang%20leaders%2C%20decide%20who%20can%20provide%20the%20best%20%26quot%3Beducation%26quot%3B%20for%20their%20child.%20To%20enroll%20in%20this%20grim%20curriculum%2C%20families%20pay%20a%20fee%20ranging%20from%20Rs%202%20lakh%20to%20Rs%203%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20children%20are%20taught%20various%20criminal%20skills%20such%20as%20pickpocketing%2C%20snatching%20bags%20in%20crowded%20places%2C%20running%20fast%2C%20evading%20the%20police%2C%20and%20also%20enduring%20beatings%20if%20caught.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20completing%20a%20year%20in%20the%20gang%2C%20the%20child's%20parents%20receive%20an%20annual%20payment%20of%20Rs%203%20to%20lakh%20Rs%205%20lakh%20from%20the%20gang%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20%26quot%3BGrand%20Theft%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20villages%20have%20produced%20some%20of%20the%20most%20cunning%20thieves%2C%20whose%20criminal%20activities%20have%20made%20headlines%20across%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%208%2C%20a%20lavish%20destination%20wedding%20at%20the%20Hyatt%20Hotel%20in%20Jaipur%20took%20a%20dark%20turn%20when%20a%20minor%20thief%20made%20off%20with%20a%20bag%20containing%20jewelry%20worth%20Rs%201.5%20crore%20and%20Rs%201%20lakh%20in%20cash.%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20grand%20event%20was%20the%20wedding%20of%20the%20son%20of%20a%20Hyderabad-based%20businessman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20ceremony%20unfolded%20and%20the%20bride%20and%20groom%20were%20being%20blessed%2C%20the%20groom's%20mother%20placed%20her%20white%20bag%20nearby.%20Seizing%20the%20opportunity%2C%20the%20minor%20thief%20discreetly%20stole%20the%20bag%2C%20making%20off%20with%20the%20valuable%20contents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20committing%20the%20theft%2C%20his%20gang%20fled%20to%20Kadiya%20village%20in%20the%20Rajgarh%20district.%20To%20avoid%20suspicion%2C%20they%20quickly%20disposed%20of%20the%20stolen%20jewelry%20and%20then%20attempted%20to%20blend%20in%20by%20participating%20in%20a%20Kanwar%20Yatra%2C%20a%20religious%20pilgrimage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20plan%20might%20have%20succeeded%20if%20not%20for%20the%20swift%20investigation%20that%20followed.%20Eventually%2C%20the%20minor%20involved%20in%20the%20theft%20was%20arrested%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20exposure%20of%20the%20entire%20gang.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20incident%2C24-year-old%20Ravindra%20Sisodia%20stole%20a%20bag%20of%20jewelry%20at%20a%20wedding%20in%20Gurgaon%20in%20March.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20December%202023%2C%20Yash%20Sisodia%2C%2022%2C%20stole%20a%20bag%20full%20of%20jewelry%20at%20a%20wedding%20ceremony%20in%20Delhi%20and%20fled%2C%20adding%20to%20his%20record%20of%2018%20cases%20registered%20against%20him%20in%20different%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EChallenges%20For%20Police%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJaideep%20Prasad%2C%20the%20Additional%20Director%20General%20of%20Police%20of%20Law%20and%20Order%2C%20said%20that%20the%20Rajgarh%20district%20is%20known%20for%20harboring%20villages%20where%20criminals%20operate%20with%20impunity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRecently%2C%20the%20Jaipur%20Police%20Commissioner%20contacted%20me%20regarding%20this%20major%20theft.%20Jewelry%20worth%20around%20Rs%201.5%20crore%20was%20stolen%20at%20a%20wedding%2C%20and%20we%20had%20reasons%20to%20believe%20the%20culprits%20were%20from%20Rajgarh.%20We%20immediately%20developed%20information%20and%20began%20coordinating%20with%20other%20states%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20these%20criminals%20are%20so%20skilled%20that%20they%20can%20assess%20the%20value%20of%20jewelry%20without%20even%20visiting%20a%20jeweler.%20Their%20primary%20activities%20include%20training%20children%20to%20steal%2C%20gamble%2C%20and%20sell%20liquor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Prasad%20emphasized%20that%20quick%20action%20and%20cooperation%20between%20state%20police%20forces%20have%20led%20to%20significant%20breakthroughs%20in%20such%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20senior%20police%20officer%20described%20the%20challenges%20faced%20by%20law%20enforcement%20in%20these%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20have%20to%20go%20to%20these%20villages%2C%20we%20take%20the%20force%20of%20several%20police%20stations%20with%20us%20to%20apprehend%20the%20accused%2C%26quot%3B%20Ramkumar%20Bhagat%2C%20the%20Inspector%20of%20the%20Boda%20police%20station%2C%20said.%20%26quot%3BThese%20criminals%20are%20highly%20trained%20in%20bag%20lifting%2C%20bank%20thefts%2C%20and%20other%20crimes%2C%20often%20using%20minors%20under%20the%20age%20of%2017%20to%20carry%20out%20their%20activities.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20these%20villages%2C%20particularly%20Kadiya%2C%20Gulkhedi%2C%20and%20Hulkhedi%2C%20are%20often%20referred%20to%20as%20%26quot%3Bnurseries%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bschools%26quot%3B%20of%20crime%2C%20where%20children%20are%20groomed%20from%20a%20young%20age%20to%20become%20professional%20thieves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMost%20of%20the%20thefts%20are%20carried%20out%20by%20minors%2C%20making%20it%20even%20more%20challenging%20to%20combat%20this%20deeply%20ingrained%20criminal%20culture%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Bhagat%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20villages%20are%20shrouded%20in%20secrecy%20and%20suspicion.%20Women%2C%20upon%20seeing%20any%20outsider%2C%20pretend%20to%20be%20hard%20of%20hearing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20an%20unfamiliar%20person%20enters%20the%20village%2C%20the%20residents%20immediately%20become%20alert%2C%20especially%20when%20they%20notice%20a%20camera%20or%20mobile%20phone.%20The%20environment%20is%20hostile%20to%20any%20form%20of%20scrutiny%2C%20reflecting%20the%20deep-rooted%20criminal%20culture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20villages%2C%20located%20in%20the%20Pachor%20tehsil%20of%20Rajgarh%20district%2C%20have%20become%20a%20hotspot%20for%20police%20forces%20from%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bhagat%20reports%20that%20over%20300%20children%20from%20these%20villages%20are%20involved%20in%20thefts%20at%20wedding%20ceremonies%20across%20various%20states.%20These%20gangs%20are%20highly%20organized%2C%20conducting%20thorough%20recces%20before%20adopting%20innovative%20tactics%20to%20carry%20out%20their%20crimes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWealthy%20individuals%20within%20the%20village%20also%20hire%20poor%20children%20for%201-2%20years%20through%20bidding%20processes%20that%20can%20reach%20up%20to%20Rs%2020%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20trained%2C%20these%20children%20often%20earn%20five%20to%20six%20times%20the%20investment%2C%20after%20which%20they%20are%20released%20from%20the%20gangs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scale%20of%20this%20criminal%20operation%20is%20massive%2C%20with%20more%20than%202%2C000%20individuals%20from%20these%20villages%20having%20over%208%2C000%20cases%20registered%20against%20them%20in%20police%20stations%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20children%20typically%20come%20from%20less%20educated%20and%20impoverished%20families%2C%20but%20they%20are%20groomed%20to%20blend%20in%20with%20the%20affluent%2C%20enabling%20them%20to%20infiltrate%20high-profile%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724145000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fv94b0mu8_school-of-criminals_625x300_20_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpay-rs-2-lakh-graduate-in-robbery-a-school-of-criminals-in-madhya-pradesh-6377136%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Three%20remote%20villages%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20-%20Kadia%2C%20Gulkhedi%2C%20and%20Hulkhedi%20-%20have%20gained%20nationwide%20infamy%20as%20%26quot%3Bnurseries%26quot%3B%20of%20criminals.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98The%20Room%20Next%20Door%E2%80%99%20Trailer%3A%20Julianne%20Moore%20and%20Tilda%20Swinton%20Play%20Estranged%20Friends%20in%20Pedro%20Almod%C3%B3var%E2%80%99s%20First%20English-Language%20Feature%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724144784000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Froom-next-door.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236111973%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20first%20footage%20from%20Spanish%20auteur%20Pedro%20Almod%C3%B3var%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Room%20Next%20Door%2C%E2%80%9D%20starring%20Oscar%20winners%20Julianne%20Moore%20and%20Tilda%20Swinton%2C%20is%20here.%20Sony%20Pictures%20Classics%20dropped%20a%20teaser%20trailer%20on%20Tuesday%20for%20the%20film%2C%20which%20marks%20Almod%C3%B3var%E2%80%99s%20first%20English-language%20feature%20and%20is%20set%20to%20premiere%20in%20competition%20at%20Venice%20Film%20Festival%20on%20Sept.%202.%20According%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Ellise%20Shafer%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fglo