0said.%20%26quot%3BI'd%20have%20to%20give%20up%20martinis%2C%20and%20don't%20ask%20me%20to%20do%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20owner%20of%20three%20restaurants%20in%20Boquete%2C%20Chris%20Young%20said%20he's%20had%20to%20balance%20increasing%20costs%2C%20pleasing%20customers%2C%20and%20avoiding%20pricing%20out%20Panamanians.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221820%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20view%20of%20Boquete%2C%20Panama.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c35ca71aa2ac29ee322566%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221365%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPeople%20walk%20down%20a%20main%20street%20in%20Boquete%2C%20Panama.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EYoung%20moved%20from%20the%20US%20about%2015%20years%20ago%20and%20arrived%20in%20Boquete%20with%20a%20restaurant%20background.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20got%20here%2C%20there%20were%20maybe%20five%20restaurants%2C'%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BNow%2C%20there's%20a%20hundred.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20bouncing%20around%20regions%20and%20jobs%2C%20Young%20and%20a%20friend%20opened%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fbigdaddysgrillboquete%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBig%20Daddy's%20Grill%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Boquete%20eight%20years%20ago.%20Since%20then%2C%20Young%20has%20opened%20two%20more%20restaurants%20in%20the%20town%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fexplore%2Flocations%2F139559905897345%2Fchristophers-american-bistro%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChristopher's%20American%20Bistro%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Ftapoutboquete%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETapOut%20Sports%20Zone%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20years%2C%20Young%20said%20he%20was%20able%20to%20sell%20meals%20for%20cheap.%20Recently%2C%20that%20has%20become%20increasingly%20difficult.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20inflation%20plays%20a%20role%2C%20he%20said%20the%20country's%20pensionado%20discount%20%E2%80%94%20a%20discount%20on%20goods%20and%20services%20for%20retirement-age%20residents%20%E2%80%94%20has%20impacted%20profitability%20in%20an%20industry%20that's%20hard%20to%20stay%20afloat.%20At%20restaurants%2C%20older%20diners%20get%2025%25%20off%20their%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYoung%20said%20his%20menus%20focus%20on%20local%2C%20typically%20inexpensive%20ingredients%20to%20keep%20food%20costs%20low.%20He's%20also%20created%20a%20taca%C3%B1o%20or%20%26quot%3Bcheap%26quot%3B%20menu%20at%20Big%20Daddy's%20Grill%20to%20appeal%20to%20Panamanians%20and%20foreigners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jackie%20Lange%20with%20tour%20guides%2C%20Jay%20and%20Jolynn.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c360ce1aa2ac29ee32277f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221349%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJackie%20Lange%20with%20tour%20guides%2C%20Jay%20and%20Jolynn.%3Cp%3EPanama%20Relocation%20Tours%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EYoung%20and%20others%20said%20the%20arrival%20of%20the%20expat%20community%20has%20also%20positively%20impacted%20Boquete.%20The%20surge%20of%20hotels%2C%20restaurants%2C%20and%20businesses%20means%20more%20job%20opportunities%20for%20Panamanians.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERios%20said%20she's%20grateful%20for%20the%20tourism%20and%20retirement%20community%20in%20Boquete.%20About%2080%25%20of%20Rios'%20patients%20are%20foreigners%2C%20and%20those%20patients%20are%20partly%20why%20her%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.odontosmileclinic.com%2Fosc%2Fosc.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOdonto%20Smile%20Clinic%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20grown%20from%20two%20employees%20to%20an%20office%20with%20two%20doctors%2C%20four%20assistants%2C%20and%20three%20specialists.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20retirees%20came%2C%20Laws%20worked%20in%20coffee%20fields%2C%20making%20%245%20da