lmart%20down%20the%20street.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20struggle%20with%20the%20change%20of%20pace%2C%20others%20love%20it.%20Christopher%20Minori%2C%2058%2C%20remembers%20moving%20to%20Boquete%20with%20his%20wife%2C%20Brandy%20Minori%2C%20in%202021%20and%20being%20shocked%20by%20how%20friendly%20and%20stress-free%20everyone%20seemed.%20It%20was%20a%20complete%20180%20from%20his%20life%20back%20in%20Georgia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20doesn't%20matter%20what%20side%20of%20the%20aisle%20you're%20on%20in%20the%20States%3B%20half%20of%20the%20country%20hates%20the%20other%20half%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20me%20over%20the%20phone.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%2C%20to%20me%2C%20stressful.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20wasn't%20the%20case%20for%20Panama.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20very%2C%20very%20mellow%20country%2C%20which%20is%20actually%20hard%20to%20get%20used%20to%20when%20you%20first%20move%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20he%20accepted%20small%20changes%20%E2%80%94%20like%20needing%20to%20ask%20a%20waiter%20for%20more%20water%20or%20understanding%20that%20a%20driver%20might%20stop%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20road%20to%20chat%20with%20a%20neighbor%20%E2%80%94%20he%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20the%20town.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20heard%20about%20Panamians'%20friendly%20and%20carefree%20attitude%20from%20every%20expat%2C%20and%20I%20witnessed%20it%20during%20my%20first%20afternoon%20in%20Boquete.%20After%20touring%20a%20coffee%20farm%2C%20the%20owners%20didn't%20call%20me%20a%20taxi%20to%20my%20hotel%20%E2%80%94%20they%20drove%20me%20there%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221232%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20view%20from%20Gabrielle%20Reynolds'%20front%20porch.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c35c651aa2ac29ee322542%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22924%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20view%20from%20Gabrielle%20Reynolds'%20front%20porch.%3Cp%3EGabrielle%20Reynolds%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ff