ttended%20the%20Shanghai%20University%20of%20Finance%20and%20Economics%2C%20where%20she%20majored%20in%20international%20business%2C%20before%20moving%20to%20the%20US%20for%20graduate%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20studied%20technology%20commercialization%20and%20management%20at%20Rensselaer%20Polytechnic%20Institute%2C%20a%20well-known%20science%20and%20engineering%20school%20in%20upstate%20New%20York%2C%20and%20later%20earned%20another%20master's%20degree%20at%20Carnegie%20Mellon%20University%20in%20computer%20science.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20of%20her%20parents%20are%20engineers%2C%20and%20Li%20said%20that%20she%20began%20exploring%20the%20world%20of%20computer%20science%20and%20engineering%20to%20satisfy%20a%20curiosity%20of%20how%20things%20are%20created.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20interested%20in%20getting%20under%20the%20hood%20and%20learning%20how%20things%20work%2C%20really%20digging%20into%20how%20things%20are%20built%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BBecause%20my%20parents%20are%20engineers%2C%20that%20mindset%20is%20not%20foreign%20to%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELi%20said%20learning%20various%20coding%20languages%20was%20a%20learning%20curve%2C%20and%20the%20time%20she%20spent%20studying%20software%20engineering%20was%20crucial%20as%20she%20moved%20into%20her%20first%20jobs%20out%20of%20college.%20After%20completing%20her%20graduate%20degrees%2C%20she%20moved%20to%20San%20Francisco%20to%20become%20a%20product%20manager%20at%20AppDynamics%2C%20an%20application%20and%20business%20monitoring%20startup%20that%20was%20acquired%20by%20Cisco%20in%202017%20for%20%243.7%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENext%2C%20she%20moved%20to%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESolvvy%2C%20an%20AI%20customer%20support%20program%20that%20was%20later%20acquired%20by%20Zoom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20didn't%20even%20know%20there%20was%20a%20'PM'%20role%2C%20but%20it%20hit%20both%20of%20the%20cores%20of%20my%20strengths%20and%20backgrounds%2C%26quot%3B%20Li%20said.%20She%20added%20that%20while%20working%20at%20Solvvy%20back%20in%202017%20and%202018%2C%20she%20had%20an%20early%20front-row%20seat%20to%20AI%20and%20machine%20learning%20at%20the%20startup%20level%2C%20which%20would%20end%20up%20serving%20her%20future%20role%20as%20an%20investor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20was%20an%20early%20startup%20in%20the%20chatbot%20space%20and%20an%20early%20sign%20of%20how%20AI%20and%20language%20models%20are%20going%20to%20change%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220045319d-88e2-4450-b95a-de2504438ad2%5C%22%3ELi%20joined%20a16z's%20infrastructure%20team%20and%20loves%20to%20invest%20in%20products%20and%20tools%20that%20help%20builders%20build.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELi's%20earliest%20exposure%20to%20the%20investing%20world%20came%20during%20a%20fellowship%20at%20Kleiner%20Perkins%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Efrom%202016%20to%202017.%20After%20getting%20to%20know%20a%20handful%20of%20successful%20VCs%2C%20including%20Kleiner%20Perkins%20partner%20Mamoon%20Hamid%2C%20former%20partner%20Andy%20Chen%2C%20and%20Asheem%20Chandna%2C%20a%20partner%20at%20Greylock%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eshe%20said%20she%20started%20mapping%20out%20potential%20career%20trajectories%20and%20thought%20she%20might%20be%20interested%20in%20moving%20to%20a%20VC%20firm%20during%20the%20back%20half%20of%20her%20career%20after%20gaining%20experience%20as%20an%20operator%20and%20potentially%20founding%20a%20startup%20herself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20chatted%20casually%20with%20a%20few%20firms%20during%20her%20years%20working%20at%20startups%2C%20but%20it%20wasn't%20until%20she%20met%20with%20investors%20at%20a16z%20while%20leading%20product%20at%20Solvvy%20that%20she%20decided%20to%20make%20an%20earlier-than-expected%20move%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELi%20officially%20joined%20a16z%20in%202018%20and%20has%20since%20been%20a%20key%20player%20in%20building%20out%20the%20firm's%20infrastructure%20team.%20The%20team%20focuses%20on%20products%20and%20tools%20that%20help%20software%20engineers%20build.%20While%20the%20team%20occasionally%20invests%20in%20chips%20and%20other%20hardware%2C%20its%20bread%20and%20butter%20is%20%26quot%3Beverything%20below%20the%20API%20level%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20with%20a%20special%20focus%20on%20developer%20tools%2C%20foundation%20models%2C%20security%2C%20and%20cloud%20startups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20more%20than%20six%20years%20she's%20been%20at%20the%20firm%2C%20Li%20says%20her%20role%20increasingly%20focuses%20on%20AI%20tools%2C%20which%20are%20transforming%20every%20stage%20of%20software%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLLMs%20and%20generative%20AI%20changed%20the%20paradigm%2C%20and%20what%20that%20means%20for%20the%20entire%20software%20stack%20%E2%80%94%20from%20testing%2C%20the%20software%20development%20life%20cycle%2C%20and%20analytics%20%E2%80%94%20is%20that%20everything%20changes%20along%20the%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELi's%20notable%20investments%20in%20the%20space%20include%20ElevenLabs%2C%20which%20develops%20synthetic%20text-to-speech%20and%20became%20a%20unicorn%20after%20a16z%20co-led%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Felevenlabs.io%2Fblog%2Fseries-b%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%2480%20million%20Series%20B%20round%20in%20early%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20and%20MotherDuck%2C%20which%20provides%20serverless%20AI%20data%20analytics%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eand%20raised%20%2447.5%20million%20across%20its%20Seed%20and%20Series%20A%20rounds%2C%20the%20latter%20of%20which%20was%20led%20by%20a16z.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20drawing%20on%20her%20software%20engineering%20background%2C%20Li%20said%20she's%20a%20better%20investor%20%E2%80%94%20even%20though%20she's%20no%20longer%20regularly%20writing%20lines%20of%20code.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20VCs%2C%20we're%20not%20as%20technical%20in%20terms%20of%20day-to-day%20writing%20code%2C%20but%20that's%20still%20a%20very%20important%20foundation%20for%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20what%20are%20the%20building%20blocks%2C%20systems%2C%20architecture%2C%20and%20pieces%3F%20Computer%20science%20helped%20with%20that%20system%20of%20thinking.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-jennifer-lis-computer-science-skills-shaped-career-at-a16z-2024-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724144401000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c36a8c1aa2ac29ee322cbc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-jennifer-lis-computer-science-skills-shaped-career-at-a16z-2024-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22a16z%20partner%20Jennifer%20Li%20leverages%20her%20computer%20science%20skills%20and%20startup%20experience%20to%20invest%20in%20AI%20infrastructure%20startups%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sstokes%40insider.com%20(Samantha%20Stokes)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-jennifer-lis-computer-science-skills-shaped-career-at-a16z-2024-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Call%20Me%20Bae%20is%20Ananya's%20riches%20to%20rags%20story%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724144296000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-112649418%2Cimgsize-33350.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fhindi%2Fcall-me-bae-trailer-ananya-pandays-riches-to-rags-story-has-a-siddhant-chaturvedi-connection-deets-inside%2Farticleshow%2F112649468.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F112649468.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%E2%80%8BIn%20the%20city%2C%20Ananya%E2%80%99s%20character%20faces%20various%20challenges%2C%20including%20living%20in%20a%20house%20with%20a%