of%20genocide%2C%20faces%20International%20Crimes%20Tribunal%20case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724144171000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-08%2F06%2Fthumb%2Ffacecrop%2F400X400%2F1722925889-3769.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fexternal-affairs-defence-security%2Fnews%2Fsheikh-hasina-accused-of-genocide-faces-international-crimes-tribunal-case-124082000545_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bangladesh's%20interim%20government%20has%20announced%20that%20it%20will%20prosecute%20those%20involved%20in%20killings%20during%20the%20mass%20student%20movement%20against%20Hasina%20in%20the%20ICT%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fexternal-affairs-defence-security%2Fnews%2Fsheikh-hasina-accused-of-genocide-faces-international-crimes-tribunal-case-124082000545_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fexternal-affairs-defence-security%2Fnews%2Fsheikh-hasina-accused-of-genocide-faces-international-crimes-tribunal-case-124082000545_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fexternal-affairs-defence-security%2Fnews%2Fsheikh-hasina-accused-of-genocide-faces-international-crimes-tribunal-case-124082000545_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Centre's%20U-Turn%20On%20Lateral%20Entry%20Amid%20Pressure%20From%20Ally%2C%20Opposition%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20today%20asked%20the%20Union%20Public%20Service%20Commission%20(UPSC)%20to%20cancel%20its%20advertisement%20for%20lateral%20entry%20into%20bureaucracy%2C%20pulling%20a%20180%20amid%20massive%20opposition%20criticism%20of%20the%20move.%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20believes%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cmove%20should%20be%20aligned%20with%20social%20justice%E2%80%9D%2C%20Union%20Minister%20Jitender%20Singh%20wrote%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20UPSC%20chief.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20Minister%20Chirag%20Paswan%2C%20whose%20LJP%20(Ram%20Vilas)%20party%20is%20a%20BJP%20ally%2C%20welcomed%20the%20move.%20Thanking%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20he%20said%20the%20move%20shows%20that%20the%20government%20listens%20to%20public%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UPSC%20last%20week%20issued%20the%20advertisement%20seeking%20%26quot%3Btalented%20and%20motivated%20Indian%20nationals%26quot%3B%20for%20lateral%20recruitment%20to%20various%20senior%20positions%20within%20the%20Union%20government.%20These%20positions%20included%20Joint%20Secretary%2C%20Director%2C%20and%20Deputy%20Secretary%20in%2024%20ministries%2C%20with%20a%20total%20of%2045%20posts%20up%20for%20grabs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20most%20of%20the%20major%20lateral%20entries%20before%202014%20were%20made%20in%20an%20ad-hoc%20manner%2C%20including%20cases%20of%20alleged%20favouritism%2C%20efforts%20of%20our%20government%20have%20been%20to%20make%20the%20process%20institutionally%20driven%2C%20transparent%20and%20open%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20minister's%20letter%20read.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Prime%20Minister%20is%20of%20the%20firm%20belief%20that%20the%20process%20of%20lateral%20entry%20must%20be%20aligned%20with%20the%20principles%20of%20equity%20and%20social%20justice%20enshrined%20in%20our%20Constitution%2C%20particularly%20concerning%20the%20provisions%20of%20reservation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELateral%20entry%20into%20bureaucracy%20refers%20to%20the%20recruitment%20of%20individuals%20from%20outside%20the%20traditional%20government%20service%20cadres%2C%20such%20as%20the%20Indian%20Administrative%20Service%20(IAS)%2C%20to%20fill%20mid%20and%20senior-level%20positions%20in%20government%20departments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20triggered%20a%20debate%20on%20lateral%20entry%20into%20bureaucracy%2C%20with%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20denouncing%20the%20process%20as%20an%20%E2%80%9Cattack%20on%20Dalits%E2%80%9D.%20The%20ruling%20BJP%20countered%20by%20pointing%20out%20that%20the%20concept%20emerged%20under%20a%20Congress-led%20government.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-is-lateral-entry-in-bureaucracy-that-triggered-bjp-vs-congress-debate-6369676%5C%22%3EWhat%20Is%20Lateral%20Entry%20In%20Bureaucracy%20That%20Triggered%20BJP%20vs%20Congress%20Debate%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lateral%20entry%20process%20was%20formally%20introduced%20during%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20tenure%2C%20with%20the%20first%20set%20of%20vacancies%20announced%20in%202018.%20This%20marked%20a%20departure%20from%20the%20traditional%20system%20where%20senior%20bureaucratic%20positions%20were%20almost%20exclusively%20filled%20by%20career%20civil%20servants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20government%20sources%2C%20the%20idea%20was%20first%20proposed%20during%20the%20UPA%20government%2C%20led%20by%20Congress%2C%20in%20the%20mid-2000s.%20In%202005%2C%20the%20UPA%20established%20the%20Second%20Administrative%20Reforms%20Commission%20(ARC)%20under%20the%20chairmanship%20of%20Veerappa%20Moily.%20The%20Commission%20was%20tasked%20with%20recommending%20reforms%20to%20the%20Indian%20administrative%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20letter%2C%20Jitendra%20Singh%20pointed%20out%20that%20while%20the%20concept%20of%20lateral%20entry%20was%20initially%20endorsed%20by%20the%20Moily%20panel%20and%20later%20supported%20by%20the%20recommendations%20of%20the%20Sixth%20Pay%20Commission%20in%202013%2C%20its%20implementation%20has%20historically%20lacked%20transparency%20and%20fairness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20PM%20Modi%2C%20reservation%20in%20public%20employment%20is%20a%20cornerstone%20of%20our%20social%20justice%20framework%2C%20aimed%20at%20addressing%20historical%20injustices%20and%20promoting%20inclusivity%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh's%20letter%20read.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20important%20that%20the%20constitutional%20mandate%20towards%20social%20justice%20is%20upheld%20so%20that%20deserving%20candidates%20from%20marginalised%20communities%20get%20their%20rightful%20representation%20in%20the%20government%20services%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh%20cited%20several%20high-profile%20cases%20where%20lateral%20entrants%20were%20appointed%20to%20key%20positions%20without%20following%20proper%20reservation%20protocols%2C%20including%20the%20leadership%20of%20the%20Unique%20Identification%20Authority%20of%20India%20(UIDAI)%20and%20even%20Secretary-level%20posts%20in%20various%20ministries%20during%20earlier%20administrations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%20these%20positions%20have%20been%20treated%20as%20specialised%20and%20designated%20as%20single-cadre%20posts%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20provision%20for%20reservation%20in%20these%20appointments.%20This%20aspect%20needs%20to%20be%20reviewed%20and%20reformed%20in%20the%20context%20of%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20focus%20on%20ensuring%20social%20justice.%20Hence%2C%20I%20urge%20the%20UPSC%20to%20cancel%20the%20advertisement%20for%20lateral%20entry%20recruitment.%20This%20step%20would%20be%20a%20significant%20advance%20in%20the%20pursuit%20of%20social%20justice%20and%20empowerment%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20letter%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpposition%20leaders%20including%20Congress%20leaders%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20accused%20the%20Modi%20government%20of%20using%20lateral%20entry%20as%20a%20backdoor%20to%20recruit%20officers%20loyal%20to%20the%20BJP's%20ideological%20mentor%2C%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS).%20In%20a%20recent%20post%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%2C%20Mr%20Gandhi%20alleged%20that%20lateral%20entry%20is%20being%20used%20to%20sidestep%20the%20UPSC%20and%20deny%20reservations%20to%20candidates%20from%20Scheduled%20Castes%20(SC)%2C%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(ST)%2C%20and%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20Union%20Minister%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%20asserted%20that%20the%20Second%20Administrative%20Reforms%20Commission%20(ARC)%2C%20chaired%20by%20Congress%20leader%20Veerappa%20Moily%2C%20recommended%20lateral%20recruitment%20to%20fill%20gaps%20in%20roles%20requiring%20specialised%20knowledge.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724144100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Ftldkseig_upsc_625x300_30_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcancel-lateral-entry-ad-minister-writes-to-upsc-head-amid-massive-row-6376565%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Union%20Minister%20Jitendra%20Singh%20today%20wrote%20to%20the%20head%20of%20the%20Union%20Public%20Service%20Commission%20(UPSC)%2C%20asking%20the%20civil%20service%20body%20to%20cancel%20its%20advertisement%20for%20lateral%20entry.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Divers%20enter%20sunken%20superyacht%20-%20but%20have%20just%20ten%20minutes%20to%20search%20for%20bodies%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724143980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F08%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-bayesian-yacht-interior_6661414.jpg%3F20240820092422%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fdivers-enter-sunken-superyacht-but-have-just-ten-minutes-to-search-for-bodies-13200100%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Divers%20have%20entered%20the%20sunken%20superyacht%20as%20they%20continue%20to%20search%20for%20the%20bodies%20of%20six%20missing%20people%2C%20but%20face%20%26quot%3Bsignificant%20challenges%26quot%3B%20during%20the%20rescue%20operation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fdivers-enter-sunken-superyacht-but-have-just-ten-minutes-to-search-for-bodies-13200100%22%2C%22c