itical%20parties%20are%20attempting%20to%20convince%20her.%20Her%20disqualification%20from%20the%20Paris%20Olympics%20due%20to%20being%20overweight%20prevented%20her%20from%20winning%20a%20gold%20medal.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Foff-the-field%2Fvinesh-phogat-may-contest-haryana-assembly-polls-against-cousin-babita-sources%2Farticleshow%2F112648454.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Perceptions%20About%20Muslims%20In%20New%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F0719a7l8_book_625x300_20_August_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%2C%20the%20reviewers%2C%20have%20faced%20this%20observation%20often%20enough%20over%20the%20years.%20Implicit%20in%20this%20statement%20is%20an%20assumption%20about%20what%20constitutes%20a%20'Bihari'.%20He%20(mostly%20'he'%20and%20rarely%20'she')%20has%20to%20be%20wild%2C%20uneducated%2C%20ill-mannered%2C%20least%20likely%20to%20be%20law-abiding%2C%20in%20constant%20pursuit%20of%20shortcuts%2C%20and%20forever%20wedded%20to%20the%20idea%20of%20%3Cem%3Ejugaad%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20observation%20might%20come%20as%20a%20compliment%2C%20it%20distresses%20us%20nonetheless.%20Being%20born%20and%20brought%20up%20in%20Bihar%20during%20a%20time%20of%20great%20political%20and%20social%20transformation%2C%20we%20rarely%20came%20across%20any%20fellow%20Bihari%20who%20fit%20this%20assumed%20definition.%20Yet%2C%20the%20assumption%20has%20persisted%20for%20years%2C%20in%20Delhi%20and%20elsewhere%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20interacted%20with%20countless%20Biharis%2C%20we%20know%20-%20to%20use%20Hilal%20Ahmed's%20distinction%20between%20discursive%20and%20substantive%20aspects%20of%20an%20identity%20-%20that%20a%20whole%20host%20of%20factors%20contribute%20to%20the%20making%20of%20a%20Bihari.%20An%20imagined%20discourse%20is%20an%20additional%20burden%20for%20every%20Bihari%20to%20deal%20with.%20The%20factors%20contributing%20to%20the%20making%20of%20a%20Bihari%20include%20caste%2C%20religion%2C%20region%2C%20educational%20background%2C%20place%20of%20residence%2C%20and%20many%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20Are%20Indian%20Muslims%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20assumption%20versus%20reality%20rule%20applies%20when%20describing%20a%20group%20of%20nearly%2020%20crore%20people%20known%20as%20Indian%20Muslims.%20Hilal%20Ahmed%20writes%2C%20%26quot%3BHistory%20of%20the%20present%20is%20perhaps%20a%20provocative%20title%2C%20especially%20when%20it%20is%20employed%20in%20relation%20to%20Muslims%20of%20India.%20It%20is%20a%20well-known%20fact%20that%20Islam%20is%20the%20second-largest%20Indian%20religion%2C%20and%20Muslims%20constitute%20almost%2014%25%20of%20the%20country's%20population.%20This%20'community%20of%20believers'%20is%20highly%20diversified-they%20are%20divided%20on%20caste%2C%20class%2C%20region%2C%20and%20even%20sub-religious%20lines.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20as%20he%20further%20notes%2C%20%26quot%3BTheir%20classification%20as%20a%20religious%20minority%20in%20purely%20statistical%20terms%2C%20the%20description%20of%20medieval%20Indian%20history%20as%20Islamic%20rule%2C%20and%20the%20media%20debates%20around%20Islamic%20jihad%20and%20terrorism%20produce%20a%20simple%20and%20undifferentiated%20image%20of%20a%20homogeneous%20Muslim%20community.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMembers%20of%20the%20community%20are%20perceived%20to%20have%20identical%20views%20on%20all%20issues%20under%20the%20sun%2C%20are%20seen%20as%20voting%20strategically%2C%20and%20are%20associated%20with%20multiple%20imagined%20%3Cem%3Ejihads%3C%2Fem%3E.%20And%20the%20list%20goes%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMuslim%20'Politicophobia'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20such%20widespread%20diversity%20is%20glossed%20over%20and%20assumptions%20are%20made%20based%20on%20stray%20events%20-%C2%A0%20fuelled%20by%20a%20heavy%20dose%20of%20%26quot%3Bglobal%20anti-Islamism%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Banti-Muslim%20communalism%20in%20the%20Indian%20context%26quot%3B%20-%20you%20have%20a%20situation%20that%20Hilal%20Ahmed%20describes%20as%20'Muslim%20politicophobia'.%20This%20leads%20to%20political%20engagement%20with%20the%20community%20being%20shunned%2C%20accusations%20such%20as%20population%20%3Cem%3Ejihad%20%3C%2Fem%3E(got%20to%20know%20this%20for%20the%20first%20time%20while%20reading%20the%20book)%20being%20levelled%20against%20them%2C%20and%20their%20representation%20in%20various%20fora%20being%20discouraged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncreased%20religiosity%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20with%20public%20displays%20of%20aspects%20of%20religion%20that%20were%20previously%20confined%20to%20the%20private%20domain%2C%20has%20further%20complicated%20the%20situation%20on%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20Different%20From%20Other%20Groups%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20these%20challenges%2C%20members%20of%20the%20community%2C%20the%20author%20argues%2C%20continue%20to%20take%20part%20in%20political%20processes%20to%20secure%20tangible%20benefits%20as%20stakeholders.%20%26quot%3BThey%20behave%20like%20consumers%2Fclients%20and%20respond%20to%20the%20welfare%20packages%20offered%20by%20political%20parties%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20writes.%20And%20in%20this%20sense%2C%20Muslims%20are%20no%20different%20from%20other%20social%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20are%20the%20ways%20then%20to%20fight%20this%20Muslim%20politicophobia%3F%20Is%20it%20all%20doom%20and%20gloom%20as%20far%20as%20Muslim%20issues%20are%20concerned%20in%20contemporary%20India%3F%20We%20couldn't%20agree%20more%20with%20the%20author's%20conclusion.%20He%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20fight%20against%20anti-Muslimism%20cannot%20be%20separated%20from%20the%20wider%20struggle%20for%20social%20justice%20and%20economic%20equality....%20One%20that%20allows%20individuals%20like%20me%20to%20critique%20economic%20injustice%20and%20social%20inequalities%20while%20adhering%20to%20my%20conception%20of%20a%20liberative%20Islam.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20book%20is%20a%20refreshing%20take%20on%20New%20India%20and%20all%20that%20it%20represents.%20There%20is%20no%20bitterness%2C%20there%20is%20no%20blame%20game.%20It%20is%20a%20foremost%20social%20scientist's%20take%20on%20the%20struggles%20and%20triumphs%20of%20Muslims%20in%20everyday%20life%20-%20their%20political%20participation%2C%20their%20survival%20strategies%20against%20odds%2C%20their%20dialogue%20with%20modernity%20and%20liberalism%2C%20and%20their%20engagement%20with%20what%20is%20called%20Muslim%20heritage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Mayank%20Mishra%20is%20Consulting%20Editor%20and%20Marya%20Shakil%20is%C2%A0Executive%20Editor%20-%20National%20Affairs%2C%20at%20NDTV)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724142060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Frqpuosk8_book_625x300_20_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fperceptions-about-muslims-in-new-india-6376665%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hilal%20Ahmed's%20book%20is%20a%20foremost%20social%20scientist's%20take%20on%20the%20struggles%20and%20triumphs%20of%20Muslims%20in%20everyday%20life%20-%20their%20political%20participation%2C%20their%20survival%20strategies%2C%20their%20dialogue%20with%20modernity%20and%20liberalism.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fperceptions-about-muslims-in-new-india-6376665%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%2