0railway%20station.%20The%20incident%2C%20discovered%20by%20the%20children's%20families%2C%20prompted%20the%20suspension%20of%20school%20staff%20and%20attracted%20political%20condemnation.%20The%20police%20faced%20criticism%20for%20delayed%20action%2C%20finally%20registering%20an%20FIR%20after%20intervention%20by%20the%20District%20Women%20and%20Child%20Welfare%20Department.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20CITY%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fmumbai%2Fmaharashtra-horror-massive-protest-near-mumbai-over-kids-molestation-at-badlapur-school%2Farticleshow%2F112642882.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BPower%20Of%20Bengal%20Government%20Shouldn't%20Be%20Unleashed%20On%20Protesters%26quot%3B%3A%20Top%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwill-set-up-national-task-force-of-doctors-on-hospital-safety-chief-justice-6375831%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topscroll%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESupreme%20Court%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20that%20it%20has%20taken%20suo%20motu%20cognisance%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkolkata-rape-murder-case-rg-kar-hospital-supreme-court-begins-hearing-in-kolkata-rape-murder-case-6375749%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKolkata%20rape-murder%20case%3C%2Fa%3E%20raises%20%26quot%3Bsystematic%20issues%20regarding%20the%20safety%20of%20doctors%20across%20India%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20bench%20headed%20by%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20said%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Bdeeply%20concerned%26quot%3B%20about%20the%20absence%20of%20safe%20working%20conditions%20for%20young%20doctors.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BIf%20women%20are%20not%20able%20to%20go%20to%20work%20and%20conditions%20are%20not%20safe%2C%20we%20are%20denying%20them%20equality%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20top%20court%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20also%20said%20that%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Bdeeply%20concerned%26quot%3B%20with%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20name%20of%20the%20victim%20has%20been%20all%20over%20the%20media%2C%20and%20the%20photographs%20and%20videos%20are%20all%20over%20the%20media.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20extremely%20concerning%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BMost%20young%20doctors%20are%20putting%20in%2036%20hours%2C%20we%20must%20evolve%20national%20protocol%20to%20ensure%20safe%20working%20conditions%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%2C%20also%20comprising%20justices%20JB%20Pardiwala%20and%20Manoj%20Misra%2C%20observed.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20court%20also%20said%20that%20it%20appears%20that%20the%20crime%20was%20detected%20in%20the%20early%20hours%20and%20that%20the%20medical%20college%20principal%20%26quot%3Btried%20to%20pass%20it%20off%20as%20suicide%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frg-kar-hospital-horror-corruption-case-against-ex-head-of-kolkata-hospital-where-doctor-was-murdered-6375590%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topscroll%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESandip%C2%A0Ghosh%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20resigned%20as%20the%20principal%20of%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20just%20two%20days%20after%20the%20incident%2C%20has%20been%20under%20scrutiny%20by%20the%20CBI%20and%20questioned%20for%20nearly%2053%20hours%20over%20the%20past%20four%20days%20regarding%20his%20actions%20following%20the%20doctor's%20death.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20conduct%20of%20the%20RG%20Kar%20Hospital's%20principal%20was%20under%20scrutiny%2C%20how%20was%20he%20appointed%20to%20another%20college%20immediately%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20asked%2C%20referring%20to%20Sandip%20Ghosh's%20appointment%20as%C2%A0the%20principal%20of%20the%20Calcutta%20Medical%20College%2C%20the%20city's%20top%20teaching%20hospital%2C%20after%20he%20resigned%20from%20the%20RG%20Kar%20Hospital.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20also%20said%20that%20the%20power%20of%20the%20West%20Bengal%20government%20should%20not%20be%20%26quot%3Bunleashed%20on%20protestors%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20time%20of%20national%20catharsis%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BThe%20West%20Bengal%20government%20was%20expected%20to%20maintain%20law%20and%20order%20and%20protect%20the%20crime%20scene%2C%20unable%20to%20comprehend%20why%20the%20state%20could%20not%20do%20so%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20top%20court%20also%20said%20that%20the%20safety%20of%20doctors%20and%20women%20doctors%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20national%20interest%20and%20the%20principle%20of%20equality%20does%20not%20demand%20anything%20less.%20%26quot%3BThe%20nation%20can't%20wait%20for%20another%20rape%20for%20it%20to%20take%20some%20steps.%20There%20are%20legislations%20in%20states%20to%20protect%20medical%20professionals%20but%20they%20do%20not%20address%20the%20systemic%20issues%2C%26quot%3B%20Chief%20Justice%20DY%20Chandrachud%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20body%20of%20the%2031-year-old%20postgraduate%20trainee%20doctor%20was%20found%20in%20the%20seminar%20hall%20of%20the%20state-run%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%20in%20Kolkata%20on%20August%209%2C%20triggering%20nationwide%20protests.%20A%20civic%20volunteer%20has%20been%20arrested%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724140200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fpvuh2r7o_supreme-court_625x300_20_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-courts-top-quotes-on-kolkata-rape-and-murder-horror-concerned-victims-identity-made-public-6375861%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20termed%20the%20rape%20and%20murder%20case%20of%20a%20trainee%20doctor%20at%20Kolkata's%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%20%26quot%3Bhorrific%26quot%3B.%20A