orkplace-safety-124082000401_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findia-news%2Fkolkata-rape-murder-case-sc-forms-task-force-for-doctors-workplace-safety-124082000401_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findia-news%2Fkolkata-rape-murder-case-sc-forms-task-force-for-doctors-workplace-safety-124082000401_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Top%20Court%20Dismisses%20Verdict%20Advising%20Young%20Girls%20To%20%26quot%3BControl%20Sexual%20Urges%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20set%20aside%20an%20order%20of%20the%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%20in%20which%20it%20acquitted%20an%20accused%20in%20a%20sexual%20assault%20case%20and%20made%20%26quot%3Bobjectionable%26quot%3B%20observations%20advising%20adolescent%20girls%20to%20%26quot%3Bcontrol%20sexual%20urges%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bench%20of%20justices%20Abhay%20S%20Oka%20and%20Ujjal%20Bhuyan%20said%20it%20has%20passed%20several%20directions%20for%20the%20authorities%20on%20dealing%20cases%20under%20the%20Protection%20of%20Children%20from%20Sexual%20Offences%20(POCSO)%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Oka%2C%20who%20pronounced%20the%20verdict%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20bench%2C%20said%20directions%20have%20also%20been%20issued%20on%20how%20the%20judgements%20should%20be%20written%20by%20the%20courts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20had%20on%20December%208%20last%20year%20criticised%20the%20verdict%20and%20termed%20as%20%26quot%3Bhighly%20objectionable%20and%20completely%20unwarranted%26quot%3B%20some%20observations%20made%20by%20the%20high%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20had%20taken%20cognisance%20of%20some%20of%20the%20observations%20made%20by%20a%20division%20bench%20of%20the%20high%20court%20and%20initiated%20a%20writ%20petition%20on%20its%20own%2C%20observing%20that%20judges%20are%20not%20expected%20to%20%26quot%3Bpreach%26quot%3B%20while%20writing%20judgements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20West%20Bengal%20government%20had%20also%20challenged%20the%20October%2018%2C%202023%20verdict%20of%20the%20high%20court%20in%20which%20these%20%26quot%3Bobjectionable%20observations%26quot%3B%20were%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20judgement%2C%20the%20high%20court%20had%20observed%20that%20female%20adolescents%20should%20%26quot%3Bcontrol%20sexual%20urges%26quot%3B%20as%20in%20the%20%26quot%3Beyes%20of%20the%20society%20she%20is%20the%20loser%20when%20she%20gives%20in%20to%20enjoy%20the%20sexual%20pleasure%20of%20hardly%20two%20minutes%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20had%20made%20the%20observations%20while%20hearing%20an%20appeal%20by%20a%20man%20who%20was%20awarded%20a%2020-year%20sentence%20for%20sexual%20assault.%20The%20high%20court%20had%20acquitted%20the%20man.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20hearing%20the%20matter%20on%20January%204%2C%20the%20top%20court%20had%20observed%20that%20certain%20paragraphs%20in%20the%20high%20court%20verdict%20were%20%26quot%3Bproblematic%26quot%3B%20and%20writing%20such%20judgements%20was%20%26quot%3Babsolutely%20wrong%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20order%20passed%20on%20December%208%20last%20year%2C%20the%20top%20court%20referred%20to%20certain%20observations%20made%20by%20the%20high%20court%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BPrima%20facie%2C%20the%20said%20observations%20are%20completely%20in%20violation%20of%20the%20rights%20of%20the%20adolescents%20guaranteed%20under%20Article%2021(right%20to%20life%20and%20personal%20liberty)%20of%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20had%20observed%20the%20issue%20before%20the%20high%20court%20was%20about%20the%20legality%20and%20validity%20of%20the%20order%20and%20judgement%20dated%20September%2019%2F20%2C%202022%20by%20which%20a%20man%20was%20convicted%20of%20offences%20under%20sections%20363%20(kidnapping)%20and%20366%20(kidnapping%2C%20abducting%20or%20inducing%20woman%20to%20compel%20her%20marriage)%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20as%20well%20as%20section%206%20of%20the%20Protection%20of%20Children%20from%20Sexual%20Offences%20(POCSO)%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20per%20the%20order%20of%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%2C%20suo%20motu%20writ%20petition%20under%20Article%2032%20of%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%20has%20been%20initiated%20mainly%20due%20to%20sweeping%20observations%2Ffindings%20recorded%20by%20the%20division%20bench%20of%20the%20high%20court%20of%20Calcutta%20in%20the%20impugned%20judgment%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20had%20said%20in%20the%20appeal%20against%20conviction%2C%20the%20high%20court%20was%20called%20upon%20to%20adjudicate%20only%20on%20the%20merits%20of%20the%20appeal%20and%20nothing%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20we%20find%20that%20the%20high%20court%20has%20discussed%20so%20many%20issues%20which%20were%20irrelevant.%20Prima%20facie%2C%20we%20are%20of%20the%20view%20that%20while%20writing%20a%20judgment%20in%20such%20an%20appeal%2C%20the%20judges%20are%20not%20expected%20to%20express%20their%20personal%20views.%20They%20are%20not%20expected%20to%20preach%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20verdict%2C%20the%20high%20court%20had%20acquitted%20the%20man%20stating%20that%20it%20was%20a%20case%20of%20%26quot%3Bnon-exploitative%20consensual%20sexual%20relationship%20between%20two%20consenting%20adolescents%2C%20though%20consent%20in%20view%20of%20the%20age%20of%20the%20victim%20is%20immaterial%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20had%20said%20it%20is%20the%20duty%2Fobligation%20of%20every%20female%20adolescent%20to%20%26quot%3Bprotect%20her%20right%20to%20the%20integrity%20of%20her%20body%3B%20protect%20her%20dignity%20and%20self-worth%3B%20thrive%20for%20the%20overall%20development%20of%20herself%20transcending%20gender%20barriers%3B%20control%20sexual%20urge%2Furges%20as%20in%20the%20eyes%20of%20the%20society%20she%20is%20the%20loser%20when%20she%20gives%20in%20to%20enjoy%20the%20sexual%20pleasure%20of%20hardly%20two%20minutes%3B%20protect%20her%20right%20to%20autonomy%20of%20her%20body%20and%20her%20privacy%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20the%20duty%20of%20a%20male%20adolescent%20to%20respect%20the%20aforesaid%20duties%20of%20a%20young%20girl%20or%20woman%20and%20he%20should%20train%20his%20mind%20to%20respect%20a%20woman%2C%20her%20self-worth%2C%20her%20dignity%20and%20privacy%2C%20and%20her%20right%20to%20autonomy%20of%20her%20body%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20high%20court%20had%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724137860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-02%2Fa1ooga8_supreme-court-of-india_650x400_14_February_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-dismisses-high-court-verdict-advising-young-girls-to-control-sexual-urges-6376204%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20set%20aside%20an%20order%20of%20the%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%20in%20which%20it%20acquitted%20an%20accused%20in%20a%20sexual%20assault%20case%20and%20made%20%26quot%3Bobjectionable%26quot%3B%20observations%20advising%20adolescent%20girls%20to%20%26quot%3Bcontrol%20sexual%20urges%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22LIVE%3A%20%26quot%3BWhat%20Were%20Police%2C%20Hospital%20Principal%20Doing%3F%26quot%3B%3A%20Top%20Court%20On%20Kolkata%20Horror%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20shocking%20rape-murder%20of%20a%20young%20doctor%20in%20Kolkata%20that%20has%20hit%20the%20country%20hard%2C%20has%20been%20taken%20up%20by%20the%20Supr