%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'What%20Was%20Principal%20Doing%3F'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20on%20its%20own%2C%20took%20up%20the%20investigation%20into%20the%20brutal%20rape%20and%20murder%20of%20a%2031-year-old%20post-graduate%20trainee%20doctor%20at%20Kolkata's%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%20on%20August%209.%20The%20incident%20has%20triggered%20widespread%20protests%20across%20the%20country%20and%20raised%20questions%20over%20women's%20safety%2C%20particularly%20in%20medical%20colleges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three-judge%20bench%20is%20led%20by%20CJI%20Chandrachud%20and%20comprises%20Justices%20JB%20Pardiwala%20and%20Manoj%20Misra.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20was%20the%20principal%20doing%3F%20FIR%20was%20not%20filed%3B%20the%20body%20was%20handed%20late%20to%20the%20parents.%20What%20is%20the%20police%20doing%3F%20A%20serious%20offence%20has%20taken%20place%2C%20the%20crime%20scene%20is%20in%20a%20hospital...%20What%20are%20they%20doing%3F%20Allowing%20vandals%20to%20enter%20the%20hospital%3F%26quot%3B%20CJI%20Chandrachud%20asked.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESandip%20Ghosh%2C%20who%20resigned%20as%20the%20principal%20of%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20just%20two%20days%20after%20the%20incident%2C%20has%20been%20under%20scrutiny%20by%20the%20CBI%20and%20questioned%20for%20nearly%2053%20hours%20over%20the%20past%20four%20days%20regarding%20his%20actions%20following%20the%20doctor's%20death.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20the%20bench's%20questions%2C%20Kapil%20Sibal%2C%20representing%20the%20West%20Bengal%20government%2C%20countered%20that%20people%20at%20the%20hospital%20had%20taken%20photos%2C%20a%20case%20of%20unnatural%20death%20was%20immediately%20started%2C%20and%20a%20board%20was%20set%20up%20with%20a%20judicial%20magistrate%20present.%20However%2C%20CJI%20Chandrachud%20said%20that%20it%20was%20the%20hospital's%20duty%20to%20file%20the%20FIR%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20absen