2%A0listing%2050%20ways%20the%20first%20Trump%20administration%20eroded%20worker%20rights%20and%20expanded%20corporate%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%20veep%20pick%2C%20Sen.%20JD%20Vance%20of%20Ohio%2C%20has%20spoken%20positively%20of%20police%20unions%20but%20denounced%20collective%20bargaining%20for%20Starbucks%20employees%20and%20opposed%20pro-labor%20measures%20during%20his%20brief%20tenure%20in%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20his%20espousal%20of%20populist%20ideals%20on%20the%20campaign%20trail%2C%20Vance%20has%20a%20history%20of%20opposing%20pro-labor%20measures.%20He%20briefly%20appeared%20on%20the%20picket%20line%20during%20last%20year's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuaw-strike-profitable-truck-suv-plants-ford-gm-stellantis-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eautoworkers%20strike%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20has%20opposed%20the%20Protecting%20the%20Right%20to%20Organize%20(PRO)%20Act%2C%20which%20would%20expand%20protections%20for%20unionizing%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHarris'%20running%20mate%2C%20Minnesota%20Gov.%20Tim%20Walz%20attacked%20Vance%20this%20month%20for%20his%20voting%20record%20on%20workers'%20rights%2C%20but%20the%20freshman%20Ohio%20senator%20has%20supported%20at%20least%20two%20pro-worker%20bills%20since%20joining%20Congress%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwashingtonpost.com%2Fpolitics%2F2024%2F08%2F15%2Fwalzs-false-claim-that-vance-never-voted-any-pro-worker-bills%2F%3Fpwapi_token%3DeyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9..EVovF_D91DZs2w2AVz6oOR2dN4FC-PX5BbqpyZdf2Fc%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Washington%20Post.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVance%20also%20cosponsored%20the%20Teamwork%20for%20Employees%20and%20Managers%20Act%2C%20a%20bill%20that%20would%20undermine%20unions%20by%20allowing%20voluntary%20%26quot%3Bemployee%20involvement%20organizations%2C%26quot%3B%20creating%20groups%20that%20wouldn't%20be%20covered%20by%20collective-bargaining%20agreements%20and%20co