%2C%20established%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiden-administration-wants-close-wage-gap-more-pay-transparency-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enew%20rules%20for%20pay%20equity%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20federal%20workers%2C%20and%2C%20in%202023%2C%20became%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpresident-biden-picket-united-auto-workers-strike-union-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efirst%20US%20president%20to%20walk%20a%20picket%20line%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20vice%20president%2C%20Harris%20repeatedly%20addressed%20unions%20and%20promoted%20pro-labor%20policies%2C%20including%20the%20bipartisan%20infrastructure%20bill%2C%20which%20invested%20in%20millions%20of%20union%20jobs%20with%20labor%20and%20wage%20protections.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWalz%20%E2%80%94%20a%20former%20school%20teacher%20and%20union%20member%20%E2%80%94%20has%20bolstered%20the%20campaign's%20pro-labor%20profile%2C%20and%20the%20Minnesota%20Gov.%20has%20been%20leaning%20into%20his%20union%20background%20on%20the%20campaign%20trail.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20call%20it%20night%20and%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20Larry%20Cohen%2C%20the%20former%20president%20of%20the%20Communications%20Workers%20of%20America%20(CWA)%2C%20the%20largest%20communications%20and%20media%20labor%20union%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20told%20BI%20about%20the%20differences%20between%20the%20Harris%20and%20Trumps%20campaigns%20on%20labor%20issues.%20%26quot%3BTrump%20and%20particularly%20Vance%20pretend%20to%20support%20a%20type%20of%20populism%2C%20but%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20workers%20who%20organize%2C%20as%20Trump%20said%20on%20his%20Twitter%20feed%20with%20Musk%20last%20Monday%2C%20when%20workers%20strike%2C%20you%20fire%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Harris-Walz%20campaign%20seems%20eager%20to%20keep%20up%20the%20reputation%20of%20supporting%20workers.%20Though%20the%20campaign%20has%20not%20yet%20rolled%20out%20its%20labor%20p