D%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FKrop-AI-2-1723817299.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Calvin%20and%20Farish%20aimed%20to%20boost%20farmers%E2%80%99%20income%20and%20resilience%20against%20climate%20fluctuations.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FKrop-AI-2-1723817299.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FKrop-AI-2-1723817299-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FKrop-AI-2-1723817299-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FKrop-AI-2-1723817299-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FKrop-AI-2-1723817299-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-361736%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ECalvin%20and%20Farish%20aimed%20to%20boost%20farmers%E2%80%99%20income%20and%20resilience%20against%20climate%20fluctuations.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarish%20continues%20to%20reiterate%20that%20Indian%20farmers%20are%20largely%20dependent%20on%20soil%2C%20water%2C%20and%20weather.%20%E2%80%9CWith%20rising%20input%20costs%20and%20poor%20yields%2C%20they%20incur%20huge%20losses%20and%20fall%20into%20subsequent%20debts.%20Hydroponics%20seemed%20a%20very%20good%20segment%20as%20it%20requires%2095%20percent%20less%20water%20and%20crops%20can%20be%20grown%20in%20a%20controlled%20environment%20with%20artificial%20light%20without%20depending%20on%20the%20weather%20outside%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Calvin%20points%20out%20that%20while%20groundwa