ame%20from%20a%20poor%20background%20and%20lacked%20formal%20cooking%20skills.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20no%20savings%2C%20and%20all%20I%20wanted%20was%20a%20job%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%E2%80%99s%20recently%20bought%20a%20scooter%20and%20expresses%20how%20thrilled%20he%20was%20at%20the%20opportunity%20to%20learn%20about%20continental%20cuisine%20while%20catering%20to%20a%20diverse%20range%20of%20customers%20each%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20signature%20dish%20is%20the%20fish%20and%20chips%2C%20complemented%20by%20a%20range%20of%20other%20offerings%20including%20falafel%2C%20salami%20and%20sausage%20sandwiches%2C%20wraps%2C%20and%20chicken%20momos.%20They%20also%20offer%20up%20to%20six%20different%20Maggi%20varieties%20and%20seven%20types%20of%20omelettes.%20The%20fresh%20Singhara%20fish%20is%20a%20favourite%20among%20visitors.%20While%20salami%2C%20bacon%2C%20and%20pepperoni%20are%20kept%20frozen%2C%20all%20other%20items%20are%20made%20fresh%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20why%20did%20they%20prioritise%20continental%20dishes%20over%20local%20cuisine%3F%20%E2%80%9CWe%20wanted%20to%20introduce%20locals%20to%20a%20different%20dining%20experience%2C%20something%20that%20deviates%20from%20their%20local%20dining%20options.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20caf%C3%A9%20serves%20a%20mix%20of%20Indian%20and%20continental%20foods%2C%20with%20chefs%20ensuring%20everything%20is%20prepared%20fresh.%20They%20start%20their%20day%20by%20making%20fresh%20tomato%20puree%2C%20and%20patrons%20have%20grown%20fond%20of%20the%20variety%20the%20caf%C3%A9%20offers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBoosted%20revenue%20for%20nearby%20shops%20and%20offered%20opportunities%20to%20locals%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20couple%20first%20arrived%20in%20Lansdowne%2C%20they%20struggled%20to%20find%20ingredients%20like%20thyme%2C%20oregano%2C%20salami%2C%20and%20sausages.%20They%20had%20to%20import%20these%20items%20from%20Delhi%20in%20ice%20boxes.%20They%20now%20source%20most%20of%20their%20supplies%20from%20a%20small%20local%20shop%20in%20Dhobighat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20shop%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20deep%20freezer%2C%20Amit%20transports%20the%20ingredients%20to%20the%20caf%C3%A9%20as%20soon%20as%20they%20arrive.%20The%20shop%2C%20noticing%20the%20success%20of%20these%20products%2C%20has%20started%20stocking%20cheese%2C%20mustard%20sauce%2C%20chocolate%20syrups%2C%20corn%20flour%2C%20and%20bread%20crumbs%E2%80%94items%20not%20typically%20used%20by%20locals.%20These%20high-margin%20products%20have%20helped%20the%20shop%20grow%20and%20attract%20other%20hoteliers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20caf%C3%A9%20now%20features%20a%20dedicated%20counter%20displaying%20handcrafted%20items%20from%20local%20women%2C%20such%20as%20knitted%20mufflers%20and%20shawls.%20This%20initiative%20helps%20them%20earn%20money%20from%20their%20homes%2C%20as%20many%20Lansdowne%20women%20knit%20but%20face%20difficulties%20selling%20their%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20pay%20them%20in%20advance%20to%20ensure%20that%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20worry%20about%20their%20items%20going%20unsold%2C%E2%80%9D%20Amit%20explains.%20This%20support%20has%20led%20to%20increased%20confidence%20among%20the%20women%2C%20who%20are%20now%20also%20making%20socks%20and%20caps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPavani%2C%20a%20local%20artisan%20who%20previously%20had%20little%20success%20selling%20her%20artificial%20jewellery%2C%20saw%20200%20of%20her%20pieces%20sell%20out%20quickly%20after%20Amit%20encouraged%20her%20to%20display%20them%20at%20the%20caf%C3%A9.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20960px)%20100vw%2C%20960px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-30-at-18.35.26_11zon-1723127605.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%2