o%20lamps%2C%20dining%20tables%2C%20and%20staircases.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20live%20on%20a%20hill%20in%20a%20delicate%20ecosystem%2C%20and%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20endanger%20the%20local%20wildlife%2C%E2%80%9D%20Amit%20explains%2C%20pointing%20out%20that%20Lansdowne%20lacks%20a%20proper%20waste%20disposal%20system.%20To%20tackle%20the%20same%2C%20they%20have%20created%20a%20pit%20to%20manage%20their%20wet%20waste%20behind%20their%20caf%C3%A9%2C%20which%20is%20then%20converted%20into%20compost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9COur%20primary%20responsibility%20is%20to%20wildlife%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20keep%20the%20forest%20vibrant%20and%20healthy%2C%20the%20couple%20has%20planted%20a%20variety%20of%20local%20flora%20including%20Banj%20Oak%2C%20Horse%20Chestnut%2C%20Kafal%2C%20Rhododendron%2C%20and%20Deodar%20Cedar.%20They%20have%20also%20set%20up%20a%20special%20birdbath%20that%20attracts%20local%20species%20such%20as%20Blue%20Whistling%20Thrushes%2C%20Black-headed%20Jays%2C%20and%20Red-billed%20Blue-Magpies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20spot%20provides%20a%20safe%20haven%20from%20larger%20predators%20like%20vultures%20and%20eagles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20many%20larger%20caf%C3%A9s%2C%20this%20one%20does%20not%20rely%20on%20genset%20generators%20for%20backup%20power.%20The%20reason%20is%20that%20these%20generators%20produce%20a%20humming%20noise%20that%20can%20disturb%20the%20local%20birdlife.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLiving%20in%20a%20forest%2C%20our%20primary%20responsibility%20is%20to%20the%20birds%2C%20leopards%2C%20mountain%20goats%2C%20wild%20boars%2C%20and%20other%20wildlife%20that%20call%20this%20place%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20Amit%20explains.%20To%20protect%20the%20surrounding%20animals%2C%20they%20keep%20the%20caf%C3%A9%E2%80%99s%20lighting%20dim%20and%20the%20music%20at%20a%20low%20volume.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20their%20offe