2C%20Jyothi%20Yarraji%2C%20the%20phenom%20hurdler%20has%20overcome%20colossal%20hurdles%20in%20her%20athletic%20journey%20to%20race%20her%20way%20to%20Paris.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFueled%20by%20grit%2C%20resilience%20and%20the%20relentless%20pursuit%20of%20dreams%2C%20Jyothi%20has%20scripted%20history%20as%20the%20first%20Indian%20woman%20to%20compete%20in%20the%20100m%20hurdles%20at%20the%20Olympics.%20After%20finishing%20seventh%20in%20her%20heat%20at%20the%20Paris%202024%20Olympics%2C%20she%20will%20now%20compete%20in%20the%20repechage%20round%20on%208%20August%2C%202024%2C%20for%20a%20place%20in%20the%20semi-final.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEarly%20life%20and%20education%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20on%2028%20August%2C%201999%2C%20Jyothi%E2%80%99s%20life%20was%20marked%20by%20simplicity%20and%20hard%20work.%20She%20grew%20up%20in%20a%20modest%20household%2C%20with%20her%20father%2C%20Suryanarayana%2C%20working%20as%20a%20private%20security%20guard%20and%20her%20mother%2C%20Kumari%2C%20as%20a%20part-time%20domestic%20help.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20combined%20income%20was%20less%20than%20Rs%2018%2C000%20per%20month.%20Despite%20their%20modest%20means%2C%20Jyothi%E2%80%99s%20parents%20always%20gave%20paramount%20importance%20to%20education.%20She%20is%20currently%20pursuing%20her%20graduation%20in%20history%20at%20Acharya%20Nagarjuna%20University%2C%20Guntur%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Jyothi%20was%20a%20student%20at%20Port%20High%20School%20in%20Visakhapatnam%2C%20her%20physical%20education%20teacher%20first%20recognised%20her%20potential.%20Her%20height%20and%20agility%20were%20seen%20as%20perfect%20attributes%20for%20a%20hurdler.%20After%20this%2C%20there%20was%20no%20looking%20back.%20Jyothi%2C%20motivated%20by%20a%20desire%20to%20support%20her%20family%20and%20driven%20by%20an%20emerging%20passion%20for%20athletics%2C%20dedicated%20herself%20to%20the%20sport.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202015%2C%20she%20first%20came%20into%20the%20spotlight%20after%20winning%20the%20gold%20medal%20at%20an%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20inter-district%20meet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EFive%20years%20of%20endless%20training%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202016%2C%20Jyothi%E2%80%99s%20journey%20took%20a%20pivotal%20turn%20as%20she%20joined%20the%20Sports%20Authority%20of%20India%20hostel%20in%20Hyderabad%2C%20setting%20the%20stage%20for%20her%20illustrious%20athletic%20career.%20Under%20the%20mentorship%20of%20Olympian%20N%20Ramesh%2C%20a%20Dronacharya%20awardee%2C%20she%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F155739%2Fkhushbir-kaur-punjab-asian-games-olympics-news%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehoned%20her%20skills%20for%20two%20rigorous%20years.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20took%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20for%20us%20to%20mould%20Jyothi%20into%20a%20hurdler.%20As%20I%20can%20remember%2C%20she%20really%20struggled%20to%20get%20tuned%20to%20the%20event.%20She%20was%20often%20covered%20in%20blood%20because%20of%20the%20rigorous%20training%20schedule.%20But%20hats%20off%20to%20her%20indefatigable%20spirit%2C%20she%20kept%20pursuing%20her%20passion%20between%202014-19%2C%20never%20complained%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ramesh%20recalled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20moved%20to%20Guntur%20in%202019%20to%20join%20the%20Centre%20of%20Excellence%20and%20eventually%20began%20training%20under%20British%20coach%20James%20Hillier%20at%20the%20Reliance%20Athletics%20High-Performance%20Centre%20in%20Bhubaneswar%2C%20Odisha.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20commitment%20showed%20dividends%20when%20she%20broke%20the%20Indian%20national%20record%20for%20the%20100m%20hurdles%20on%2010%20May%2C%202022%2C%20with%20a%20time%20of%2013.23%20seconds.%20This%20achievement%20was%20just%20the%20beginning.%20Jyothi%20went%20on%20to%20break%20her%20own%20record%20multiple%20times%2C%20continually%20pushing%20the%20boundaries%20of%20her%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EOne%20historic%20record%20after%20another%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMirroring%20the%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F258400%2Findia-first-female-olympic-mary-dsouza-sequeira-hockey-women-history%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20obstacles%20she%20overcomes%20on%20track%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Jyothi%E2%80%99s%20career%20as%20a%20hurdler%20has%20faced%20its%20own%20formidable%20hurdles.%20The%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20and%20a%20debilitating%20back%20injury%20severely%20limited%20her%20participation%20in%20competitions.%20The%20following%20year%2C%20the%20Commonwealth%20Games%20in%20Birmingham%20proved%20disappointing%20as%20she%20failed%20to%20advance%20past%20the%20first%20round%2C%20finishing%2010th.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20these%20setbacks%2C%20Jyothi%20ended%202022%20on%20a%20high%20note%20by%20clinching%20gold%20in%20the%20100m%20hurdles%20at%20the%20National%20Games.%20Although%20this%20time%20didn%E2%80%99t%20qualify%20as%20a%20national%20record%20due%20to%20wind%20assistance%20(%2B2.5m%2Fs)%2C%20it%20marked%20her%20as%20the%20first%20Indian%20woman%20to%20dip%20below%20the%2013-second%20mark%20in%20the%20100m%20hurdles.%20At%20the%20same%20National%20Games%2C%20she%20also%20won%20gold%20in%20the%20100m%2C%20defeating%20top%20sprinters%20Dutee%20Chand%20and%20Hima%20Das%2C%20with%20a%20record-setting%20time%20of%2011.51%20seconds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20momentum%20continued%20at%20the%20National%20Open%20Athletics%20Championships%202022%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20where%20she%20bettered%20her%20national%20record%20with%20a%20time%20of%2012.82%20seconds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20Jyothi%E2%80%99s%20impressive%20streak%20of%20performances%20continued%20both%20domestically%20and%20internationally.%20She%20secured%20a%20silver%20m